ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: The general class of the information supplied: information; exception; accident, employment; onset, etc.

ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: System and code pertaining to the specific information regarding special conditions relating to the setting, treatment or patient  for which care is sought.

ivardefs.name: reason
ivardefs.desc: Provides the reason in the situation where a reason code is required in addition to the content.

ivardefs.name: sequence
ivardefs.desc: A number to uniquely identify supporting information entries.

properties.desc: Additional information codes regarding exceptions, special considerations, the condition, situation, prior or concurrent issues.
